Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懼怕神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下有強大的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我化身完美無缺的神的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡面聚集著活化了細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些細胞不是普通人的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEEDLESS的細胞麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEEDLESS的DNA有和常人不一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就把那些部分聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把肉體變成神的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵NEEDLESS的目的不單單是為了收集能力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果要活化那麼多細胞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該需要龐大的能量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是利用了由磁場生成器吸收的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dean Drive F.H.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊全打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過  你和我的潛力差的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dean Drive F.H.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熔岩灼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就呆在那裡乖乖看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後好好品嚐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈辱和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE  SECOND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻  此處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.60,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃亮亮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將由神來統治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們NEEDLESS的世界終於要到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  特殊能力只需要神擁有就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要讓各位消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特大人變成神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是會創造NEEDLESS的世界麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是會創造沒有爭鬥的世界麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這麼堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然抱怨神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就從你開始消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.34,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脆弱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連對你忠心耿耿的NEEDLESS也要消滅麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你是神  你認為這種事能被原諒麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗軍的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個沒有能力的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在BS存活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且現在對身為神的我提出異議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到光榮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你的生命將要終結在我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是本大人的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺他先得經過本大人的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快把你的手放開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那裡好好看著你那重要的「僕人」痛苦地死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就咒罵自己的無能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁界·山田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋引力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該讓他受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犍陀多蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你們NEEDLESS就是廢渣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們掠奪了神的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有點比常人厲害的能力也不要太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德  你是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己是多麼無能多麼無意義的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  該和你那群愚蠢的同伴們一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  愚蠢的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道伊甸的蘋果出問題了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要拒絕我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為長年都寄宿在樓閣寺璃琉的身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有變質的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入了與原型不同的伊甸的蘋果的關係麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你後悔麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有和我相遇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會遇到阿克萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會陷入這樣的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是和這些扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論走哪條路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會有絆腳的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是妨礙到我的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要踢飛它繼續走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  你恢復知覺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這傢伙讓我醒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.17,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提神香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼弱還要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我治療了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個紅豆年糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說阿克萊特麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和他吵架了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  一直給你們添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.39,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犍陀多蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紋紋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dean Drive F.H.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未央醬·防護牆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.93,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  庫魯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是統一戰線哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們的話是救不了那位大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離地上三百米左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特在最頂上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他睡著了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁界·反發  防禦網
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  治療完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  好好地幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復一下狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種閒工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特體內的正向回饋正在急劇不斷地發生著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會發生大爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本會不留痕跡地被炸飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計剩下的時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在的戰力是不可能打倒阿克萊特的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼  老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.86,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘娘腔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了是麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你最喜歡說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞路佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  你心裡的某處還想著是否有得救的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止的人生裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無數次將絕望掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  你卻活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是使用你能力的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說庫魯斯君是NEEDLESS麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.26,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現新事實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是亞路佳大人的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒什麼不可思議的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直瞞著我們麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯君沒有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的力量並不是單單是指能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在BS活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯不斷的磨練出來的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是超人的觀察力和卓越的推理能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經被他救過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確至今為止很多次都是被庫魯斯的提議給救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人如果沒有姐姐在身邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對自己更有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也結識了那麼多夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在活在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味地沉溺在自己的能力中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了尋求力量而接近阿克萊特的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始發狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拯救大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爆炸了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為我治療下姐姐的傷勢麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是想殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼想法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定找出擊敗阿克萊特的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只等你一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好短
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次引發逆排斥反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得引發逆排斥反應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的能力都將被封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣或許就能覓得勝機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣呢  但是…
